status.description: Represents the status of the phone number entry upload on Microsoft Teams.

error_code.description: A code returned by Microsoft Teams if there is an error with the phone number entry upload.

error_message.description: A message returned by Microsoft Teams if there is an error with the upload process.

civic_address_id.description: Identifies the civic address assigned to the phone number entry.

location_id.description: Identifies the location assigned to the phone number entry.

internal_status.description: Represents the status of the phone number entry upload on Telnyx.
